  <p><strong>PAYMENT TERMS</strong><br />
  Standard terms of payment are Net 30 days. We also accept VISA, Mastercard, American Express, and Discover credit cards.</p>
  <p><strong>PRIVACY POLICY</strong><br />
    In the process of conducting business with customers, Reliable Imaging   may collect information, such as but not limited to, customer's  name, company name, title, phone number, e-mail address, site name, URL and address. </p>
  <p>Reliable Imaging will use collected information to fulfill orders, information requests, and to improve our products and services. At no time will Reliable Imaging  sell customer information to third parties.</p>
  <p><span><strong>RETURN POLICY</strong><br />
    Reliable Imaging  will work with a location on a return.  The return policy is thirty (30) days unconditional; after that, six (6) months exchange for either upgraded equipment (i.e., no longer using the same printers), or defective product.</span></p>
